               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction (fols. 3r-8v)&#xD; - The “Synopsis of classes” (fols.
                     3r-4r)&#xD; - Letter of Eusebius to Carpianus (fols. 4v-5r)&#xD; - Canon Tables
                     (fols. 5v-8v) &#xD; II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 9ra-42v) &#xD; - List of the
                     “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 53 titles (fols. 9ra-10vb) &#xD; - Bǝsrāta
                     Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (Mt. 1-17:4) (fols. 11ra-42vb), incomplete &#xD;
                     &#xD; Additiones 1-5.</summary>
